  EffectDiscription_ENG: "Burst Digivolve: 0 from [Rosemon] by returning 1 [Yoshino
    Fujieda] to handAt the end of the burst digivolution turn, trash this Digimon\u2019s
    top card[When Digivolving] Suspend 1 of your opponent's Digimon and 1 of their
    Tamers. Until the end of your opponent's turn, all of their Digimon and Tamers
    don't unsuspend. [When Attacking] Trash the top card of your opponent\u2019s
    security stack for every 2 of your opponent's suspended Digimon and Tamers."
